description:
Formed in 2010, the American Lust Junkies have established themselves in the los angeles area as a force to be reckoned with. 
Fronted by nick davis, guitars by thomas kantin, bass is anthony dehaven, drums are nick ganz. 
The core members have been in several projects together in the L.A. scene. This band is a groove filled hard rock band who blends the sounds of the 90s with a harder edge. 
Hope you like it!
